1526	## 5. Comparative Synthesis
1527	
1528	### 5.1 Oscillator Algorithm Comparison
1529	
1530	| Algorithm     | Aliasing | CPU/voice | Memory | Pitch flexibility | Complexity |
1531	|--------------|----------|-----------|--------|-------------------|------------|
1532	| Naive        | Severe   | ~1 ns     | None   | Any              | Trivial    |
1533	| PolyBLEP     | Good     | ~5 ns     | None   | Any              | Low        |
1534	| MinBLEP      | Excellent| ~20 ns    | 1-4 KB | Any             | Medium     |
1535	| Additive     | None     | O(K) sines| None   | Any              | Medium     |
1536	| Wavetable    | Good*    | ~10 ns    | 100 KB+| Limited by table | Low-Med    |
1537	
1538	*Quality depends on mipmap table design.
1539	
1540	### 5.2 Filter Topology Comparison
1541	
1542	| Topology          | Slope      | Self-osc | Nonlinear | Stability | Web Audio native |
1543	|------------------|-----------|---------|-----------|----------|-----------------|
1544	| Biquad (RBJ)     | 12 dB/oct | No      | No        | Always   | Yes (BiquadFilterNode) |
1545	| 4-pole cascade   | 24 dB/oct | No      | No        | Always   | No (custom)     |
1546	| Chamberlin SVF   | 12 dB/oct | Yes     | No        | fc<Fs/6  | No              |
1547	| ZDF SVF          | 12 dB/oct | Yes     | No        | Always   | No              |
1548	| Moog Ladder (HL) | 24 dB/oct | Yes     | Yes (tanh)| Always   | No              |
1549	| MS-20 (SK)       | 12 dB/oct | Yes     | Yes (clip)| Always   | No              |
1550	
1551	### 5.3 Reverb Approach Comparison
1552	
1553	| Approach         | CPU  | Memory | Realism | Control | Latency       |
1554	|-----------------|------|--------|---------|---------|---------------|
1555	| ConvolverNode   | High | High   | High    | Limited | Block-size    |
1556	| Freeverb        | Low  | Low    | Medium  | Full    | Zero          |
1557	| FDN (Feedback Delay Network) | Medium | Low | High | Full | Zero |
1558	
1559	### 5.4 Polyphony Model Comparison
1560	
1561	| Model          | Max voices | CPU overhead | Expressiveness |
1562	|---------------|-----------|-------------|----------------|
1563	| Monophonic    | 1         | Minimal     | Legato/slides  |
1564	| Paraphonic    | N (shared filter) | Low | Limited       |
